source:
TEXT_BANARK128_04578_SEQ_00Maru reeds a resupply for a bustling business.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANARK128_04578_SEQ_00 Schwierigkeitsanpassung (Job/Klasse darf nicht gewechselt werden)

Maru möchte die Lebensmittelvorräte auffüllen.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_TODO_00<tab>Place the fragrant fish at the designated locations and slay any Akyaali crabs that appear.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_TODO_00<tab>Einen duftenden Fisch auslegen, um Akyaali-Krabben anzulocken

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the Akyaali crab legs to Maru.

TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_000<tab>The meyhane has drawn people of all stripes to our little corner of the realm, and for that I'm grateful. That bein' said, the strain on our supplies grows with every new face, and I need your help to stave off an impendin' shortage.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_000<tab>Die Schenke ist gut besucht, worüber wir uns sehr freuen. Das hat allerdings dazu geführt, dass wir viel mehr Lebensmittel für die Küche brauchen. Kannst du uns bei der Beschaffung helfen?

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_001<tab>I'm talkin' about Akyaali crab legs─as popular as they are pointy! Still, the creature that bears 'em should be easy prey for you. I reckon they'll know it, too, so don't be stingy with the bait if you want 'em to come scuttlin'.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_001<tab>Wir hätten gerne <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E91D6030502 /var>. Wenn du <var 32 ((EventItem)) 02F61E91D5020502 /var> an der Küste auslegst, kannst du damit <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 02F22C4F020502 /var> anlocken.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_002<tab>Just to be on the safe side, you'd best set down three of these fish, eh? Space 'em out, too, so as to better your chances. Safe huntin', friend.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_002<tab>Das klappt leider nicht jedes Mal. Versuch es ruhig an drei Stellen.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_SYSTEM_000_003<tab>There don't appear to be any hungry crabs in the area.
TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_004<tab>Ah, there you are. I hope you had a chance to enjoy the spray of salt water on your face durin' your hunt. Did you get the legs?
TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_005<tab>Ah, yes... These are exactly what I was lookin' for. Thank you for bringin' me such fine specimens─we'll feed many a hungry Hippo Rider with these.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_005<tab>Ah ja, genau danach habe ich gesucht! Vielen Dank!

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_006<tab>...An' plenty of visitors besides, no doubt. Not a lot of cooks linin' up to duel those spindly buggers, even if their meat makes for some of the most mouthwaterin' seafood on the island.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_006<tab>Die Beine von Akyaali-Krabben haben kräftige Muskeln und sind sehr schmackhaft.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_007<tab>Toss 'em in a curry and their flavor still sings through the spices, or throw 'em in a biryani for some delightful texture. And that's just the beginnin'...
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_007<tab>Ich mag sie am liebsten gut gewürzt mit Curry als Biryani-Reis.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_008<tab>'Course, if they ain't fresh, they ain't nearly as tasty, so it may not be long before we're needin' more. Until then!
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_008<tab>Sie müssen aber absolut frisch sein und können daher nicht lange gelagert werden. Vielen Dank, dass du uns bei der Jagd geholfen hast!
